        <Summary>A Gimp resources thumbnailer</Summary>
        <Description>GimpResourcesThumbnailer is a thumbnail service for KDE. It can be used in any KDE application that supports the thumbnail kioslave, like Dolphin or digiKam. You can preview all of your GIMP resources like brushes and patterns, to easily manage them into folders, without the need to open GIMP.</Description>
